EditorConfig

https://github.com/sindresorhus/editorconfig-sublime#readme

1. Install EditorConfig using package control and restart sublime
CTRL + SHIFT + P, Install Package, EditorConfig

2. Create ".editorConfig" file with the required settings.


HTML/JS/CSS - prettify

.jsbeautifyrc file (directory containing src file to be prettified or its parent and so on or home directory)
Check right click -> HTML/JS/CSS Prettify -> Set Prettify settings
Shortcut : CTRL + SHIFT + H
